::Skulletron::

            Skulletron waited for a few minutes.  By now, they 
probably would've taken her to a CR Chamber.  He ran to the 
Cybertronian Fire entrance.  He didn't wait, so he decided to use his 
com.

                "Greetings Maximals.  My name is Skulletron, and I am 
here to serve you unquestioningly.  I come in peace, so let me in and 
I will explain more about myself," He said, calmly.
